trans-unit.source: Defines the behavior for the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> associated with a <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WorkflowServiceHost" />.
trans-unit.target: Define el comportamiento del <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> asociado con un <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WorkflowServiceHost" />.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior> to access the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> object in your workflow service.
trans-unit.target: Utilice <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior> para tener acceso al objeto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> del servicio de flujo de trabajo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> object is added by default when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WorkflowServiceHost> is created.
trans-unit.target: De manera predeterminada, se agrega el objeto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> cuando se crea el <xref:System.ServiceModel.WorkflowServiceHost>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior" />.

trans-unit.source: This constructor sets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior.CachedInstanceExpiration%2A> property to 10 minutes.
trans-unit.target: Este constructor establece la propiedad <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior.CachedInstanceExpiration%2A> en 10 minutos.

trans-unit.source: Configures the workflow service to support the workflow run-time behavior.
trans-unit.target: Configura el servicio de flujo de trabajo de modo que admita el comportamiento en tiempo de ejecución del flujo de trabajo.

trans-unit.source: This method creates a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior.CachedInstanceExpiration%2A> extension and configures it for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime>.
trans-unit.target: Este método crea una extensión <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WorkflowRuntimeBehavior.CachedInstanceExpiration%2A> y la configura para el <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates how long a workflow instance stays in-memory in the idle state before it is forcibly removed from memory.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece un valor que indica cuánto tiempo permanece en memoria una instancia de flujo de trabajo en estado inactivo, antes de quitarla obligatoriamente.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> object indicating how long a workflow instance stays in-memory in the idle state before it is forcibly removed from memory.
trans-unit.target: Un objeto <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> que indica cuánto tiempo permanece en memoria una instancia de flujo de trabajo en estado inactivo, antes de quitarlo obligatoriamente.

trans-unit.source: Verifies the scheduling service used for workflow services has been added to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> object and that the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> object has not started before the call to <see cref="Overload:System.ServiceModel.Channels.CommunicationObject.Open" />.
trans-unit.target: Comprueba que el servicio de programación, utilizado para los servicios de flujo de trabajo, se ha agregado al objeto <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" />, y que el objeto <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> no se inicia antes de llamar a <see cref="Overload:System.ServiceModel.Channels.CommunicationObject.Open" />.

trans-unit.source: The wrong <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService" /> is registered.
trans-unit.target: Se registra el <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService" /> equivocado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> associated with a <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WorkflowServiceHost" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> asociado con una instancia <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WorkflowServiceHost" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Un objeto <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> object is not initialized before retrieving this property, then a new <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> object is created.
trans-unit.target: Si no se inicializa el objeto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> antes de recuperar esta propiedad, se crea un nuevo objeto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime>.
